ok at this pen, it's black pen. This is the best pen out there, never runs out of ink. I mean, this is an unbelievable pen. Fuck the fuck, right, it's a pen. The question though is, how can I sell you a pen if I first don't know what you want? So the first thing I would do, I would reverse it, so tell me, how long you've been in the market for a pen? Are you even looking for a fucking pen? I don't waste my time trying to sell things to people that don't need them or want them. That's the biggest mistake that young salespeople make. I connect with all the millionaires and billionaires that interview, could I get your contact? Yeah, sure.",
